nodes.text: Kaydine was a captain in the Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps in 1 ABY. He was Naboo's most decorated starfighter pilot, president of the Flying Color Guard, the Chamcellor-elect of the Naboo Betterment Society and an all-round local celebrity. From Theed Palace, he set a spacer a number of tasks combating the Ay'Nat pirates.
